Description: Fragment of limestone bearing a royal head in sunk relief.
Curator's comments: S. Dhennin, Mefkat et la déese Hathor. Topographie et religion dans le IIIe province de Basse Egypte, MIFAO 146, Cairo 2022, p. 108 no. 11 (discusses dating: Nectanebo II based on style or Ptolemy II based on other fragments).
